🔹 LinkService kya hai?
LinkService ek service class hai jo Identity aur Application ke beech ka connection (Link object) manage karta hai.

👉 Matlab:-
Identity (user)
Application account (jaise AD, DB, SAP)
In dono ke beech jo mapping hoti hai → usko Link bolte hain
Aur usko handle karta hai → LinkService.

🔹 LinkService kya kya karta hai?
Identity ke saare accounts nikalta hai
Specific application ka account nikalta hai
Entitlements (groups/roles) fetch karta hai
Link create/update/delete karta hai
Aggregation ke baad account sync karta hai.
----------------------------------------------------------------
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
()🔹 2. “Aggregation ke baad account sync karta hai” ka matlab?
--🔹 2. “recouncilation vs sync kya karta hai?

👉 Isko step by step samajh:-
🔥 STEP 1: Aggregation kya karta hai?
👉 Application se data uthata hai
Example:-
AD se 1000 users laaye
DB se 500 accounts laaye

🔥 STEP 2: Reconciliation (Mapping):-
👉 Har account ko kisi Identity se match karta hai
Match mila → Link ban gaya
Match nahi mila → Uncorrelated account

🔥 STEP 3: Sync (yaha LinkService ka role aata hai)?
👉 Sync ka matlab:-
Database me Link ko update / maintain karna
🧠 Example:-
()Pehle:-
Rahul → group: User

()Aggregation ke baad:-
Rahul → group: Admin + User

👉 Ab kya karega system?
➡️ LinkService:-
purana link check karega
naya entitlement add karega
DB me update karega

🔹 Simple Line me dono ka difference 👇
Term	             Matlab
Reconciliation:-----Account ko identity se match karna
Sync:---------------Link ko update/maintain karna
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------[
🔹 Kya ye DB me store hota hai? 🤔
👉 YES bhai ✅
Link object database me store hota hai
Table: mostly spt_link
Isme kya hota hai:-
identity_id
application_id
nativeIdentity (username)
attributes (JSON/XML format)
entitlements
👉 Jab bhi aggregation hota hai:-
Application se data aata hai
Link table me save/update hota hai.

🔹 Simple Flow:-
Aggregation run hua
Account mila (AD, DB, etc.)
Link create/update hua
LinkService usko manage karta hai.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
getLinks(Identity identity)
getLinks(Identity identity, Application application)
getLink(Identity identity, Application application)
getLinkById(String id)
getLinkByNativeIdentity(Application application, String nativeIdentity)
getLinksByApplication(Application application)
getLinksByIdentity(Identity identity)
